You can use your Apple Account balance to purchase games and other apps in the Apple Store app. It’s safe to buy App Store & iTunes Gift Cards on FunPay because the seller won’t get the payment right away. After the buyer pays for the order, the payment is put on hold by the security system and is transferred to the seller only after the buyer redeems the gift card and confirms the order completion.

  2. Pay for the order and get a gift card.
  3. Redeem the gift card and confirm the order completion.
